<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 13. Male genitalia of Pseudophanias excavatus A ventral view B lateral view C dorsal view D tergite VIII E sternite VIII. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." , "Figure 12. Male antenna of Pseudophanias excavatus by SEM images A lateral view B ventral view C antennomere 11 in ventral view D antennomeres 5 - 10 in ventral view E special setae on antennomere VIII in ventral view. Scale bars: 0.2 mm (A, B); 0.1 mm (C, D); 0.01 mm (E)." , "Figure 9. Dorsal habitus of Pseudophanias excavatus A male B female. Scale bar: 1.0 mm." , "Figure 10. Morphological details of Pseudophanias excavatus A habitus in lateral view B male antenna C female antenna D male metaventrite. Scale bars: 1.0 mm (A); 0.5 mm (D); 0.2 mm (B, C)." , "Figure 11. SEM images of Pseudophanias excavatus, male A head B maxillary palp C pronotum D metaventrite E elytra F abdomen G protarsus H protarsal claws. Scale bars: 0.2 mm (A, C-F); 0.1 mm (B, G); 0.05 mm (H)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472467" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472464" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472465" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472468" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/472466" .

